WEBVTT

00:00:04,180 --> 00:00:06,300
Not being able to use your computer

00:00:06,300 --> 00:00:09,260
because you mouse doesn't work is frustrating.

00:00:09,260 --> 00:00:12,720
Many people use only the keyboard to navigate websites.

00:00:12,720 --> 00:00:16,140
Either through preference or circumstance.

00:00:16,140 --> 00:00:19,340
Whether it's temporarily limited mobility

00:00:19,340 --> 00:00:21,580
a permanent physical disability

00:00:21,580 --> 00:00:23,580
or simply a broken mouse

00:00:23,580 --> 00:00:25,580
the result is the same

00:00:25,580 --> 00:00:29,520
Websites and apps need to be operable by keyboard.

00:00:31,060 --> 00:00:33,020
Web accessibility

00:00:33,020 --> 00:00:36,800
Essential for some, useful for all.
